OL,3,CFormer Berkshire GP found guilty of
OL,4,Cstring of indecent assaults against
OL,5,Cpatients
OL,7,FA GP has been found guilty of a string
OL,8,Fof indecent assaults against seven
OL,9,Fpatients in Berkshire.
OL,11,FStephen Cox, 65, was found guilty of
OL,12,F12 counts of indecent assault and
OL,13,Facquitted of a further four following
OL,14,Fa four-week retrial at Reading Crown
OL,15,FCourt, Thames Valley Police said.
OL,17,FThe force said that over a number of
OL,18,Fyears Cox repeatedly indecently
OL,19,Fassaulted seven of his female patients
OL,20,Fon the pretext of carrying out routine
OL,21,Fmedical examinations.
