OL,5,Cpatients
OL,7,FCox claimed he did not remember any of
OL,8,Fthe patients, the force said, and
OL,9,Fdenied the allegations, saying it was
OL,10,Feither misunderstanding, an accident,
OL,11,For that his victims were not telling
OL,12,Fthe truth.
OL,14,FInvestigating officer Detective
OL,15,FConstable Sara Di Giorgio said Cox had
OL,16,Fbetrayed the trust of his patients.
OL,18,F"These offences occurred many years
OL,19,Fago, over a period of time in the
OL,20,F1980s and 1990s," she said.
